posts.post_content: Looking for 1910 Obak T212 - Vancouver team player cards, Raw or graded in good/VG+ condition. Please no emails, PM me 1st. Thanks, Brad

Hand cut scrap….NFS.

But best of luck on your search!

Greetings from Vancouver Island. I forget if I already showed you my Van & Vic Obaks. Put the bunch together a decade or so ago. Victoria shortstop Ward was my toughie. Good luck in the hunt. Here is a link to my cards: [url]https://tinyurl.com/4xpaacf6[/url] pw = vanvic
